{
  "text": "2 Further, because y * is unobserved, we do not actually estimate the \u03b1's. Rather, we estimate parameters called \u03b2's. As [CITATION_1] , citing Amemiya [1985 ) notes, the \u03b1's and the \u03b2's are related this way:",
